            "title": "Overview",
            "level": 1,
            "blocks":
            [
                {
                    "paragraph": "Gladiator Beast is a toolbox deck that requires a monster to attack or survive an attack in order to be returned to the deck for another Gladiator monster. These monsters have various effects between destroying monsters or spell and trap cards, gaining attack or attacking twice. The deck focuses on heavy backrow and trap cards and is more of a control deck."
                }   
            ]
        },
